title: GE 25.3 Cu. Ft. Side By Side Refrigerator GSS25GGH
description:
Features:

Integrated shelf support system
Provides strong, flexible support
Adjustable slide-out, spillproof glass shelves
Raised edges help contain spills and make clean up quick and easy
Fresh food multi-level drawers
Provides the ideal environment for storing your fruits and vegetables
Adjustable door bins
Creates additional storage space for milk and other gallon-size containers
Arctica icemaker
A special access door puts ice within reach
Advanced water filtration uses MWF replacement filter
Removes trace pharmaceuticals from water and ice* and uses replacement filter MWF (*Removes ibuprofen, atenolol, fluoxetine, progesterone and trimethoprim. These pharmaceuticals are not necessarily in all users’ water)
